{
  "id": "adv_event_2403_01_04",
  "title": "仙台＆札幌",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――サニーピース全国ツアーin仙台",
      "translations": {
        "en": "— Sunny Peace National Tour in Sendai",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 1.5800000906,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_04-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "前方、敵影なし……！　大丈夫、誰もいない……\n今の内に体育館の扉の近くへ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The coast is clear…! Okay‚ there’s no one around…\nNow’s our chance‚ to the gym doors…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.5000000398,
      "endTime": 10.1068027894,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.2934695323
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_04-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ、別にここまでコソコソしなくても\nいいんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ we don’t have to be this sneaky‚\ndo we?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.2934695323,
      "endTime": 15.173469456100001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.360136199
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_04-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "しーっ！　静かに……体育館には生徒が大勢いる……\n私達の存在がバレたら、騒ぎになる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shh! Be quiet… There are a lot of students in the gym…\nIf our presence is revealed‚ there will be a commotion…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.360136199,
      "endTime": 22.861542201,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.048208944
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_04-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "サプライズだもんね\nバレないように気をつけないと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s a surprise‚\nso we have to be careful not to be noticed…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.048208944,
      "endTime": 27.9740367333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.1607034762
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_04-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "極秘潜入だね！\nなんだかスパイ映画みたいでワクワクするよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A top-secret infiltration!\nThis feels like a spy movie‚ it's so exciting~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.1607034762,
      "endTime": 34.3972569545,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.5940368096
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_04-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "全校生徒が集まってる体育館に、私達がサプライズで\n登場するなんて……どんな反応になるか楽しみね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Imagine if we suddenly appear in the gym where all students gathered\nas a surprise… I can't wait to see their reactions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.5940368096,
      "endTime": 44.053197423600004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.2398641665
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_04-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "それは……まぁ、私も楽しみだけど……\nそ、そんなことより、今日の段取りを確認するわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… yeah‚ I’m looking forward to it too though…\nA-Aside from that‚ let’s confirm the schedule for today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.2398641665,
      "endTime": 54.4507032474,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 54.6398641665
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_04-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "これから会う相手は、さくらのファンなのよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The person we're going to meet now is your fan‚ Sakura‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.6398641665,
      "endTime": 58.759864099699996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.9731974999
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_04-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "うん。高校の吹奏楽部の子なんだけど\n演奏会でサニピの曲を演奏してくれたんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. They are in the high school brass band club‚\nand they played a Sunny Peace song at their concert.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.9731974999,
      "endTime": 66.5761454979,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.7731974999
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_04-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "演奏会の動画、観た……サニピの曲を\nみんなで一生懸命演奏してて……感動した……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I watched the video of the concert… They played Sunny Peace’s song\nall together with such passion… It was really moving…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.7731974999,
      "endTime": 74.8531977097,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.0398644526
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_04-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "そこで先生方にお願いして、今日の全校集会で\n演奏してもらうことになったのよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ they perform at today’s school assembly\nas we asked the teachers‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.0398644526,
      "endTime": 81.23236246900001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.419029212
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_04-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "部員達は部活動の一環だと思って\n何も知らずに私達の曲を演奏し始める……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The club members just think it’s part of their club activities‚\nso they’ll start playing our song without any information…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.419029212,
      "endTime": 88.7078502416,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.919029212
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_04-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "そこにサニーピースがいきなり登場して\n歌い出すんだよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And then Sunny Peace suddenly appears\nand starts singing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.919029212,
      "endTime": 93.9248793363,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.119029212
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_04-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "全校生徒が見てる前で、体育館のステージに立って\n吹奏楽部の生演奏で歌う……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Standing on stage in the gym‚ with the entire student body watching‚\nand singing to the live music of the brass band…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.119029212,
      "endTime": 102.7907075644,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.9856958787
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_04-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ～……サプライズ喜んでくれるかな～？\n想像しただけでドキドキしてきたよ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mmm… I wonder if they’ll like the surprise?\nJust imagining it makes me excited~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.9856958787,
      "endTime": 112.533405153,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 112.719029212
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_04-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "みんなの思い出に残る、最高のステージにしようね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s make it the best stage‚ one that will stay in everyone’s memories!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.719029212,
      "endTime": 117.3916822195,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.5783489625
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_04-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "もうすぐ演奏が始まる……そろそろ出番……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The performance will start soon… It’s almost our turn…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.5783489625,
      "endTime": 121.0078727166,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 121.1945394595
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_04-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、サプライズがバレないように\n小さな声でいくよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚ to keep the surprise a secret‚\nlet’s go in with quiet voices.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.1945394595,
      "endTime": 126.507691582,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
